'''飓风亚历克斯'''是1955年[[1954年12月飓风爱丽丝|飓风爱丽丝]]过后首场在一月形成的[[北大西洋热带气旋|大西洋飓风]]，源自2016年1月7日[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]附近的低气压，此时尚[[温带气旋|不具备热带天气系统特征]]。系统起初向东北移动，于1月8日经过[[百慕大|百慕大]]后转向东南并逐渐增强。1月10日，气旋风速一度达到飓风强度，然后小幅减弱并蜿蜒向东行进，后又改朝东北飘移。随着时间的推移，系统逐渐发展出[[热带气旋|热带天气系统特征]]，于1月12日在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]以南较远处海域转变成[[副热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]，成为2006年[[热带风暴泽塔|热带风暴泽塔]]过后北大西洋第一个在一月成型的热带或亚热带气旋。风暴转向东北偏北并继续朝热带天气系统发展，于1月14日完成转变，并达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时140公里，[[气压|中心最低气压]]981[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.97[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，按[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级]]属一级飓风。1月15日，亚历克斯弱化成强热带风暴并[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[特塞拉岛|特塞拉岛]]，而且此时已开始失去热带天气系统特征，离开亚速尔群岛朝海上进发数小时后就转变成温带气旋，最终于1月17日同[[拉布拉多海|拉布拉多海]]上空的另一个气旋融合。

受亚历克斯的前身影响，百慕大1月7日至9日天气恶劣。面对飓风逼近，气象机构向亚速尔群岛发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风和热带风暴警告]]，当地学校及商铺、企业暂时关闭。亚速尔群岛降下暴雨并有强烈阵风，但建筑受到的损伤程度很轻，另有一人因天气恶劣无法及时就医死于[[心肌梗死|心脏病发]]。

== 背景及纪录 ==
根据气象机构现有定义，每年的大西洋飓风季都是从6月1日开始，11月30日结束，绝大多数北大西洋热带气旋都是这段时间形成<ref>{{cite book | url = https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | author = Neal Dorst | agency = Hurricane Research Division | title = Frequently Asked Questions | version = 4.11 | editor1 = Chris Landsea | editor2 = Neal Dorst | date = 2016-06-02 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | chapter-url = https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/G1.html | chapter = G1) When is hurricane season? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190809193313/https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | archivedate = 2019-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不在飓风季内形成的热带气旋统称[[淡季大西洋飓风列表|淡季热带气旋]]，大部分是在5月或12月成型<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | type = Database | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT) | version = 2 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-060415.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2015-06-04 | accessdate = 2016-01-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160113090727/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2014-060415.txt | archivedate = 2016-01-13 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。1月极少形成热带气旋，除亚历克斯外，1851年开始有可靠纪录至今也只出现过五次，分别是1938年一场未命名的飓风，1951年一场未命名的热带风暴，1954年12月形成并一直持续到次年1月的[[1954年12月飓风爱丽丝|飓风爱丽丝]]，1978年一场亚热带风暴，以及2005年12月形成并持续到次年1月的[[热带风暴泽塔|热带风暴泽塔]]<ref name="WU3">{{cite web | author = Jeff Masters | website = Weather Underground | date = 2016-01-13 | accessdate = 2016-01-15 | title = Unprecedented: Simultaneous January Named Storms in the Atlantic and Central Pacific | url = http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=3222 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160115030905/https://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=3222 | archivedate = 2016-01-15}}</ref>。由于爱丽丝是在12月形成，因此亚历克斯就成为1938年那场未命名飓风过去至今唯一在1月成型的大西洋飓风<ref name="WU3" /><ref name="D4">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Hurricane Alex Discussion Number 4 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.004.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117203402/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.004.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

亚历克斯以强热带风暴强度登陆[[特塞拉岛|特塞拉岛]]，是1955年飓风爱丽丝（登陆[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]和[[萨巴|萨巴]]）后第一个登陆过的北大西洋热带气旋<ref name="WU">{{cite web | author = Bob Henson | date = 2016-01-15 | title = Astounding Alex Hits the Azores: January's First Atlantic Landfall in 61 Years | url = http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=3224 | website = Weather Underground | accessdate = 2016-01-16 | archivedate = 2016-01-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160116103247/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=3224}}</ref>。与大部分热带气旋相比，亚历克斯的形成位置也很罕见，是有确切纪录以来第二个在[[北纬30度线|北纬30度]]以北、[[西经30度线|西经30度]]以东形成的大西洋飓风<ref>{{cite web | author = Mike Carlowicz | publisher = National Aeronautics and Space Administration | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = An Atlantic Hurricane... in January | url = https://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/images/87324/an-atlantic-hurricanein-january | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160120132450/http://earthobservatory.nasa.gov/NaturalHazards/view.php?id=87324 | archivedate = 2016-01-20 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。此外，亚历克斯还是2012年[[2012年大西洋飓风季|飓风戈登]]过后首场影响亚速尔群岛的飓风。该群岛周边370公里海域往年只在8至9月会有热带气旋经过，亚历克斯是至今仅有的例外。<ref name="Reuters">{{cite news | author = Andrei Khalip | agency = Reuters | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2016-01-15 | title = Hurricane Alex hits Azores less hard than feared | url = https://www.reuters.com/article/us-storm-alex-idUSKCN0UT192 | archivedate = 2016-01-15 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6eYlWfzDQ?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-storm-alex-idUSKCN0UT192}}</ref><ref name="TWC">{{cite web | publisher = The Weather Channel | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Rare January Hurricane Alex Landfalls in The Azores as a Tropical Storm | url = https://weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/hurricane-alex-atlantic-ocean-azores | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160115012932/http://www.weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/hurricane-alex-atlantic-ocean-azores | archivedate = 2016-01-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

亚历克斯发展成型之际，中太平洋形成[[2016年太平洋颶風季|飓风帕里]]。这是有纪录以来大西洋和太平洋首次一起在1月发展出热带气旋。<ref name="WU3" />

== 发展历程 ==
{{storm path|Alex 2016 track.png}}
2016年1月初，西[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]存在大规模[[滞留锋|滞留锋]]，并于6日在[[古巴|古巴]]西北边境上空催生出低气压<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Eric S. Blake | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2016-09-13 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Hurricane Alex | series = Tropical Cyclone Report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL012016_Alex.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181112224229/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL012016_Alex.pdf | archive-date = 2018-11-12 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="CIMSS">{{cite web | author = Scott Bachmeier | work = CIMSS Satellite Studies | publisher = Cooperative Institute for Meteorological Satellite Studies (CIMSS) | date = 2016-01-13 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Hurricane Alex | url = https://cimss.ssec.wisc.edu/satellite-blog/archives/20483 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118105540/http://cimss.ssec.wisc.edu/goes/blog/archives/20483 | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。次日，低气压朝东北方向的[[高速气流|副热带高速气流]]移动，并与[[高空槽|短波槽]]相互影响，在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东北方向的下层大气中形成旋转扰动气流<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="WU1" />。这股气流继续北大逼近[[百慕大|百慕大]]，但因包括[[风切变|风切变]]强、[[海面温度|海面温度]]低在内的不利因素影响而无法朝热带天气系统转变<ref name="TWO1"/><ref name="WU1">{{cite web | author = Bob Henson | work = Weather Underground | date = 2016-01-07 | accessdate = 2016-01-08 | title = Rare January Depression in Central Pacific; Atlantic Subtropical Storm Next Week? | url = http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=3218 | archivedate = 2016-01-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160108204727/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=3218}}</ref>。系统的[[烈风|烈风]]强度风场很大，[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]在每小时95至100公里范围<ref name="TWO1">{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1016-01-07 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook (3:25 PM EST – Thu Jan 7, 2016) | series = Tropical Weather Outlook Atlantic | archivedate = 2016-01-31 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2016/TWOAT.201601072025.txt | format = .TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131085214/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2016/TWOAT.201601072025.txt}}</ref>。1月8日，系统在百慕大以北约120公里洋面经过，岛上因此遭遇狂风暴雨<ref name="TRG1">{{cite news | author = Jonathan Bell | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | date = 2016-01-08 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Windy weather affects flights and power | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160108/NEWS/160109802 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160112211125/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160108/NEWS/160109802 | archivedate = 2016-01-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。次日，系统受此时非常罕见的气流格局[[阻塞高气压|阻挡]]无法继续向东北移动，因此转向东南偏东，进入外界环境更有利于发展[[副热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的海域<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="TWO3">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-09 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook (3:00 PM EST – Sat Jan 9, 2016) | series = Tropical Weather Outlook Atlantic | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2016/TWOAT.201601091959.txt | format = .TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131092444/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2016/TWOAT.201601091959.txt | archivedate = 2016-01-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。1月10日，系统核心下方的地面气压降至979 [[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.91[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），周围环绕的风力达到飓风强度<ref name="TCR" />，与此同时上层大气中出现的暖芯表明气旋结构更趋对称<ref name="MWR_2018">{{cite journal | author1 = Juan Jesús González-Alemán | author2 = Jenni L. Evans | author3 = Alex M. Kowaleski | journal = Monthly Weather Review | date = 2018-10 | title = Use of Ensemble Forecasts to Investigate Synoptic Influences on the Structural Evolution and Predictability of Hurricane Alex (2016) in the Midlatitudes | volume = 146 | issue = 10 | pages = 3143–3162 | doi = 10.1175/MWR-D-18-0015.1 | bibcode = 2018MWRv..146.3143G}}</ref>，只是中心附近的[[对流|对流]]依旧稀疏<ref name="TWO4">{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-10 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Special Tropical Weather Outlook (1:50 PM EST – Sun Jan 10, 2016) | series = Tropical Weather Outlook Atlantic | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2016/TWOAT.201601101848.txt | format = .TXT | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160131124153/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOAT/2016/TWOAT.201601101848.txt | archivedate = 2016-01-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。受中大西洋上空的[[低压槽|中纬度低压槽]]影响，气旋同[[高速气流|高速气流]]分离后大幅转向东南偏南<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="WU3" />，进入水温比常年一月平均值高1.5°C（2.7°{{lang|en|F}}）左右的海域<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite web | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | agency = Marine Modeling and Analysis Branch | date = 2016-01-10 | accessdate = 2019-08-09 | title = [Atlantic Sea Surface Temperature Anomalies for January 10, 2016] | url = https://polar.ncep.noaa.gov/sst/ophi/archive/20160110/nwatl_anomaly_ophi0.png | format = .PNG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190809215121/https://polar.ncep.noaa.gov/sst/ophi/archive/20160110/nwatl_anomaly_ophi0.png | archivedate = 2019-08-09 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

1月11至12日，系统结构朝[[副热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]转变，边缘的[[锋_(气象)|锋]]同核心分离<ref name="TCR" />，核心变得更对称<ref name="MWR_2018" />并与[[冷心低压|上层低气压]]共存而且位置基本重叠{{refn|group=注|气旋核心与上层低气压处在同一位置可以为亚热带气旋所需对流提供能量<ref>{{cite web | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2019 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = [Subtropical Cyclone] | series = Glossary of NHC Terms | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml#s | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190912164011/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutgloss.shtml#s | archivedate = 2019-09-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。|name=ULL}}，环流顶部发展出的对流层虽然很薄，但对流已经足够强劲<ref name="TCR" />{{refn|group=注|冬季天气寒冷，纬度越高的海域对流活动越少，[[对流层顶|对流层顶]]随纬度减少而降低，这反过来又令天气系统关联的对流发展受限。相比之下，夏季温度回暖，对流发展频繁，对流层顶也就随之升高。<ref>{{cite web | author1 = B. Geerts | author2 =  E. Linacre | publisher = University of Wyoming | date = 1997-11 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = The height of the tropopause | url = http://www-das.uwyo.edu/~geerts/cwx/notes/chap01/tropo.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061230163041/http://www-das.uwyo.edu/~geerts/cwx/notes/chap01/tropo.html | archivedate = 2006-12-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author1 = Günther Zängl | author2 = Klaus P. Hoinka | journal = Journal of Climate | number = 14 | volume = 14 | pages = 3,117–3,139 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0442(2001)014<3117:TTITPR>2.0.CO;2 | date = 2001-01 | title = The Tropopause in the Polar Regions | bibcode = 2001JCli...14.3117Z}}</ref>}}。这些因素都表明气旋到[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]1月12日下午18点时已完成向亚热带气旋的转变，风暴此时位于[[加那利群岛|加那利群岛]]西南偏西约1850公里洋面，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]用“亚历克斯”（{{lang|en|Alex}}）为其命名<ref name="TCR" />。受此前令气旋朝南转向的低压槽影响，风暴接下来一天先向东北偏东前进，后转至东北偏北<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="D1">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-13 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Subtropical Storm Alex Discussion Number 1 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.001.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117193457/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.001.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

风暴[[雨带|螺旋带]]中很快出现[[風眼|类风眼结构]]，表明亚历克斯还在增强<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="D2">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Subtropical Storm Alex Discussion Number 2 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.002.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118013821/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.002.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。1月14日，气旋内呈现出宽25公里的类风眼结构，周围云层基本对称，云顶温度低至−60°{{lang|en|C}}（−75°{{lang|en|F}}）<ref name="D4" /><ref name="D3">{{cite report | author = Stacy Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Subtropical Storm Alex Discussion Number 3 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.003.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118001817/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.003.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。接下来系统开始同上方的上层低气压分离，进入风切变较弱的海域，进而令暖芯温度进一步升高，并发展出上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]，两者均为热带天气系统的常见特征<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="D3" />。虽然行经海域水温只到22°{{lang|en|C}}（72°{{lang|en|F}}）左右{{refn|group=注|通常来说，要满足维持热带气旋内部对流及环流的能量需求，海面温度至少要达到26.5°{{lang|en|C}}（80°{{lang|en|F}}）<ref>{{cite book | url = https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | author = Chris Landsea | agency = Hurricane Research Division | title = Frequently Asked Questions | version = 4.11 | editor1 = Chris Landsea | editor2 = Neal Dorst | date = 2018-06-01 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | chapter-url = https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/A15.html | chapter = A15) How do tropical cyclones form? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190809193313/https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqHED.html | archivedate = 2019-08-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，但气象学家对热带气旋和海面温度的研究结果表明，海面温度并非热带气旋形成的充分和必要条件。以本条目所述的亚历克斯为例，其他大气因素对形成热带气旋作用更大，中纬度洋面由温带或亚热带气旋转变成的热带气旋更是如此。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Jenni L. Evans | journal = Journal of Climate | date = 1993-06 | title = Sensitivity of Tropical Cyclone Intensity to Sea Surface Temperature | volume = 6 | issue = 6 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0442(1993)006<1133:SOTCIT>2.0.CO;2 | pages = 1,133–1,140 | bibcode = 1993JCli....6.1133E}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author1 = Lloyd J. Shapiro | author2 = Stanley B. Goldenberg | journal = Journal of Climate | date = 1998-04 | title = Atlantic Sea Surface Temperatures and Tropical Cyclone Formation | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-climate_1998-04_11_4/page/578 | volume = 11 | issue = 4 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0442(1998)011<0578:ASSTAT>2.0.CO;2 | pages = 578–590 | bibcode = 1998JCli...11..578S}}</ref>}}，但风暴还在继续强化，到{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}1月14日早上六点已完全转变成热带气旋<ref name="TCR" />。这主要是因为亚历克斯所在海域的[[对流层|对流层]]上层气温比赤道附近海域低，令大气环境变得更不稳定<ref name="D4" /><ref name="TCR" />。[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克卫星估算]]结果表明，风暴转变后已达飓风强度。不久，亚历克斯达到最大持续风速每小时140公里，中心最低气压981毫巴（百帕，28.97英寸汞柱）的最高强度，按[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级]]属一级飓风。<ref name="TCR" />

1月14至15日，气旋在北上逼近亚速尔群岛期间因水温降低、风切变增多开始减弱<ref name="D5">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Hurricane Alex Discussion Number 5 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.005.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118013826/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.005.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="D6">{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Hurricane Alex Discussion Number 6 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.006.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118004829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.006.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。类风眼结构周围的对流消退，表明亚历克斯已开始转变回温带气旋<ref name="D6" />。气旋结构因风切变影响渐趋混乱<ref name="D8">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Tropical Storm Alex Discussion Number 8 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.008.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118001828/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.008.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，减弱成热带风暴后，亚历克斯于{{lang|en|UTC}}15日下午13:15[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[特塞拉岛|特塞拉岛]]<ref name="TCR" />。不到五小时后，风暴已完全转变成温带气旋，环流变得细长，[[最大风速半径|最大风速半径]]扩大，边缘再度同锋关联<ref name="TCR" />，并且整体结构在锋的影响下更像“逗号形状”<ref name="D9">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2016-01-15 | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Alex Discussion Number 9 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.009.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118004835/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.discus.009.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。转向北上朝[[格陵兰|格陵兰]]进发期间，系统略有增强，气压降至978毫巴（百帕，28.88英寸汞柱）。气旋同格凌兰东南沿海的多山地形相互影响，岛上风力普遍达到飓风强度。{{lang|en|UTC}}1月17日早上6点左右，亚历克斯的残留被北大西洋上空更大规模的温带低气压系统引收。<ref name="TCR" />
