== 防灾措施和影响 ==
=== 百慕大 ===
受亚历克斯的前身影响，百慕大1月7日至9日天气恶劣，[[L·F·韦德国际机场|百慕大国际机场]]前后三天共降雨34毫米<ref name="BerCli">{{cite report | title = Daily Climatology Written Summary: January 1 2016 to January 31 2016 | publisher = Bermuda Weather Service | date = 2016-01 | series = Monthly Climate Reports | at = [http://weather.bm/climate.asp Report for January 2016 retrieved through Climate Data Search Interface]}}</ref>。1月8日，时速97公里的阵风导致树木倒塌，753户居民家中停电，航空运输也受到影响。高达六米的巨浪触发[[小型船只警告|小型船只警告]]，各岛轮渡暂停。<ref name="TRG1" /><ref>{{cite news | work = Bernews | date = 2016-01-08 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Windy Conditions Cause Power Outages | url = http://bernews.com/2016/01/753-customers-power-dut-weather/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190806134134/http://bernews.com/2016/01/753-customers-power-dut-weather/ | archivedate = 2019-08-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | date = 2016-01-08 | accessdate = 2020-04-17 | title = Ferries suspended | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160108/NEWS/160109800 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160111113642/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160108/NEWS/160109800 | archivedate = 2016-01-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

=== 亚速尔群岛 ===
[[File:Alex's_final_waves_over_Azores.jpg|right]]
1月14日亚历克斯成为飓风后，亚速尔群岛气象局向[[法亚尔岛|法亚尔岛]]、[[皮库岛|皮库岛]]、[[圣若热岛|圣若热岛]]、[[格拉西奥萨岛|格拉西奥萨岛]]和特塞拉岛发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]，同时向[[圣米格尔岛|圣米格尔岛]]和[[圣玛丽亚岛|圣玛丽亚岛]]发布热带风暴警告<ref name="PA4">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-14 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Hurricane Alex Advisory Number 4 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.public.004.shtml | type = Advisory | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160117193503/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.public.004.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。群岛中部和东部岛屿收到红色警报，这也是当地最高级别的天气警报<ref name="Publico">{{cite news | author = Ana Dias Cordeiro | agency = Lusa News Agency | newspaper = Público | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Furacão Alex passou a tempestade tropical depois de ter atravessado os Açores | url = https://www.publico.pt/2016/01/15/sociedade/noticia/acores-sem-incidentes-nos-primeiros-efeitos-do-furacao-alex-1720289  | archivedate = 2016-01-15 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6eYmbXDmD?url=http://www.publico.pt/sociedade/noticia/acores-sem-incidentes-nos-primeiros-efeitos-do-furacao-alex-1720289?page=-1 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。面对狂风暴雨威胁，居民堆叠[[沙袋|沙袋]]防止房屋进水，并在门窗外加装挡风板。风暴期间，政府官员将学校及行政办公楼封闭。<ref name="Reuters" />[[萨塔亚速尔航空|萨塔亚速尔航空]]取消1月15日早上的33架次国内和国际航班，滞留旅客超过700人<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = The Tribune | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Hurricane Alex Weakens After Passing Azores | url = http://www.tribune242.com/news/2016/jan/15/hurricane-alex-weakens-after-passing-azores/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160125154356/http://www.tribune242.com/news/2016/jan/15/hurricane-alex-weakens-after-passing-azores/ | archivedate = 2016-01-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Renascença | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Pico e São Miguel já sentem o furacão "Alex", mas "nada de monta" | url = https://rr.sapo.pt/2016/01/15/pais/pico-e-sao-miguel-ja-sentem-o-furacao-alex-mas-nada-de-monta/noticia/44275/ | archivedate = 2016-01-17 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6eakQWPhV?url=http://rr.sapo.pt/printArticle.aspx?objid=1c869e8a-80bb-e511-b837-0022640e86b7 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。1月15日风暴过境后，飓风和热带风暴警告中止生效<ref name="PA8">{{cite report | author = Richard Pasch | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Tropical Storm Alex Advisory Number 8 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.public.008.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118004911/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2016/al01/al012016.public.008.shtml | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

1月15日经过亚速尔群岛期间，亚历克斯令多个岛降下暴雨并伴有强烈阵风<ref name="Reuters" />。圣米格尔岛[[拉古阿_(亚速尔群岛)|拉古阿]]降水总量103毫米<ref>{{cite web | work = Weather Underground | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Lagoa IAZORESL2 | url = https://www.wunderground.com/dashboard/pws/IAZORESL2/graph/2016-01-15/2016-01-15/daily | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190727194839/https://www.wunderground.com/dashboard/pws/IAZORESL2/graph/2016-01-15/2016-01-15/daily | archivedate = 2019-07-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，特塞拉岛的[[英雄港|英雄港]]也有94毫米<ref>{{cite web | work = Weather Underground | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Santa Luzia meteo IANGRADO6 | url = https://www.wunderground.com/dashboard/pws/IANGRADO6/graph/2016-01-15/2016-01-15/daily | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190727054407/https://www.wunderground.com/dashboard/pws/IANGRADO6/graph/2016-01-15/2016-01-15/daily | archivedate = 2019-07-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。圣玛丽亚岛的阵风风速超过每小时80公里，整个群岛以圣米格尔岛[[蓬塔德尔加达|蓬塔德尔加达]]所测阵风时速最高，达到92公里<ref name="TWC" /><ref name="CIMSS" />。狂风刮倒树木，导致部分房屋屋顶受损，另有局部停电。风暴引发轻度洪灾，<ref name="Reuters" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Sarah Lagan | title = Residents' fears for families as storm hits | date = 2016-01-16 | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160116/NEWS12/160119725 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118001713/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20160116/NEWS12/160119725 | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>蓬塔德尔加达六户民宅受损，另有一户人家的屋顶被毁<ref>{{cite web | publisher = TVI 24 | date = 2016-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Açores: furacão "Alex" causou 43 ocorrências | url = https://tvi24.iol.pt/geral/29-01-2016/texto | archivedate = 2016-01-17 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6eb8vRFn8?url=http://www.tvi24.iol.pt/geral/29-01-2016/texto | deadurl = no}}</ref>。群岛中部岛屿发生多处[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，但造成的损失很小<ref name="Publico" />。整体而言，亚历克斯的破坏程度不及预期<ref name="Reuters" />，这可能是因为当时风暴已开始转变成温带气旋，最强风力远离气旋中心<ref name="TCR" />。此外，因风暴产生的湍流导致急救直升机无法及时起飞，当地一人死于心脏病发<ref>{{cite news | agency = Lusa News Agency |newspaper= Público | date = 2016-01-16 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Furacão Alex impede socorro da Força Aérea e doente morre | url = https://www.publico.pt/2016/01/16/sociedade/noticia/furacao-alex-impede-socorro-da-forca-aerea-e-doente-morre-1720408 | archivedate = 2016-01-17 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/6eb9KEHSq?url=https://www.publico.pt/sociedade/noticia/furacao-alex-impede-socorro-da-forca-aerea-e-doente-morre-1720408 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | publisher = Government of the Azores | date = 2017-10 | accessdate = 2020-04-18 | title = Identificação e Avaliação de Impactes, Vulnerabilidades e Opçōes de Adaptação às Alteraçōes Climáticas | agency = Programa Regional de Alteraçōes Climáticas dos Açores | url = http://servicos-sraa.azores.gov.pt/grastore/DSMALL/PRAC/RelatorioAdaptacao_SegurancaPessoasBens_VersaoConsultaPublica.pdf | page = 48 | format = .pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190727040358/http://servicos-sraa.azores.gov.pt/grastore/DSMALL/PRAC/RelatorioAdaptacao_SegurancaPessoasBens_VersaoConsultaPublica.pdf | archivedate = 2019-07-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

